 ROTC component will conduct individual  pin on  ceremonies in designated areas on VMI Post in accordance with their service traditions  Pinning Ceremonies will be held in the following locations  Army ROTC  Marshall Hall  Center for Leadership   Ethics  Naval ROTC   Barracks area  Jackson Arch Area  Air Force ROTC   Jackson Memorial Hall Cameron Hall will be the location for inclement weather    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 